    Suitable For: Suitable for daily use. Suitable for vegan.

    Boxed Contents: 24 Powder Sachets

    Size: 24 Pack

    Serving Size: 1 sachet (4g) per 200mL water

    Servings Per Pack: 24 sachets

    Warnings

    Berocca Sport is a formulated supplementary sports food to be consumed in conjunction with a nutritious diet and appropriate physical training or exercise program. Not a sole source of nutrition.

    Not suitable for children under 15 years of age or pregnant women: should only be used under medical or dietetic supervision.

    Adults and children 15 years and over, 1 powder sachet dissolved in 200mL of water. Take daily or as directed. Not a sole source of nutrition and should only be consumed in conjunction with a nutritious diet and appropriate physical training or exercise program.

    STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

    Do not use if sachet is open or broken. Store in a cool dry place, below 25°C.

    Recycle

    Recyclable Packaging?: Yes

name: Aptamil Essensis Organic A2 Protein Milk 2 Premium Follow-On Formula From 6-12 Months 900g
description:
Information

General Information

Aptamil Essensis 2 Premium Follow-On Formula is our most exclusive organic A2 protein milk formulation*:


  • Patended synbiotic blend
  • Organic A2 protein milk sourced from certified organic farms in New Zealand
  • Formulated to meet the nutritional needs of babies from 6 months to 1 year of age

    • *Within the Danone and Nutricia ANZ range
    Certified Organic By AsureQuality Limited

    Aptamil Essensis 2 Premium Follow-On Formula combines our unique patented synbiotic blend with organic A2 protein milk, making it our most exclusive formulation, to help build strong foundations for your baby's future.

    • Patented synbiotic blend^
    • Organic A2 protein milk sourced from certified organic farms in New Zealand
    • Product manufactured and certified organic in New Zealand
    • Scan QR code on the bottom of the can for product tracing
    • 900g tin format


    ^Refer to ingredients
    Certified Organic By AsureQuality

    Size: 900g

    Warnings

    Breast milk is best for babies. Before you decide to use this product, consult your doctor or health worker for advice.

    Meets the nutritional needs of formula fed infants as part of a mixed diet.

    Follow instructions exactly. Prepare bottles and teats as directed. Do not change proportions of powder except on medical advice. Incorrect preparation can make your baby very ill. Infants over 6 months should be offered foods in addition to infant formula product. Not for use for infants under 6 months.

    Dental Hygiene: Putting your baby to bed with a bottle can cause tooth decay. Encourage your baby to drink from a cup from 6 to 8 months.

    Do not use if security foil is damaged or missing.

    Ingredients

    Organic milk solids, organic vegetable oils (emulsifier (organic soy lecithin), antioxidant (natural tocopherols (soy))), organic short chaingalacto-oligosaccharides (milk), dried omega LCPUFAs (fish oil, antioxidant (sodium ascorbate, natural tocopherols (soy))), long chain fructooligosaccharides,taurine, inositol, choline chloride, Bifidobacterium breve M-16V (570 million cfu/100mL), L- carnitine.

    Minerals: Potassium, calcium, chloride, phosphorus, sodium, magnesium, iron, zinc, copper, iodine, manganese, selenium.

    Vitamins: Vitamins (A, B1, B3, B5, B6, B12, C, D3, E, K1), folic acid, biotin.

    Nucleotides: Cytidine-5'-monophosphate, uridine-5'-monophosphate, adenosine -5'-monophosphate, inosine -5'-monophosphate, guanosine-5'-monophosphate.

    Aptamil Essensis Organic A2 Protein Milk Premium Follow-on Formula is based on cows' milk protein.

    Contains: Contains: cows' milk, fish and soy.

    Allergen Contains: Fish| Milk| Soy

    Directions

    Feeding Guide -
    Age: 6-8 months,
    Cool boiled water: 180mL,
    Level scoops of powder*: 6,
    Number of feeds per day: 3-5.

    Age: 9-12 months,
    Cool boiled water: 180mL,
    Level scoops of powder*: 6,
    Number of feeds per day: 3-4.

    *1 scoop = 4.5g of powder. NOTE: 1 scoop of powder added to 30mL of water yields approximately 33mL of formula. This feeding guide is a general guide ONLY; your baby may need more or less than shown.

    PREPARATION INSTRUCTIONS

    1. Wash hands before preparing the feed. Clean and then sterilise all utensils by boiling for 5 minutes or using an approved steriliser.

    2. Boil safe drinking water and allow to cool to feeding temperature. CONSULT FEEDING GUIDE. Measure the required volume of water into a sterilised feeding bottle.

    3. Use only the enclosed scoop. Fill the scoop lightly and level off using the built-in leveller. Avoid compacting the powder.

    4. Always add one level scoop of powder for each 30mL of water. Cap the bottle and shake briskly to dissolve the powder.

    5. Test temperature on wrist before feeding. Feed immediately (do not store). Discard unfinished feeds.

    Prepare each bottle separately. It is safer to use Aptamil Essensis Follow-On Formula immediately after it is prepared.

    STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

    Store in a cool dry place. Use by the date on container bottom. After opening, keep container airtight and use contents within four weeks.

    Product is packed by weight, not volume. Some settling of the powder may occur during transportation and distribution.

    RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

    Recycle.

    Recyclable Packaging?: Yes

Information

Why Choose Performance Isolate?

Performance Isolate is a single source, ultra-filtered protein made using only whey protein isolates.

Starting with the highest quality whey protein, the raw material undergoes a series of sophisticated separation processes to remove excess fat, cholesterol, sugars and other materials until all that remains is the purest form of protein.

Lean Growth

Support the growth and maintenance of muscle.

Repair

Rebuild and repair muscle fibres used during intense exercise.

Recover

Support muscle recovery after exercise.

Whey Protein Isolates

A single source, ultra-filtered protein made using only whey protein isolates.

Natural EAAs

EAAs can promote more effective muscle repair as they help in supporting muscle protein synthesis.

High Purity

We utilise a series of sophisticated filtration processes to 'isolate' out excess fat, cholesterol and sugar.

Informed Choice

We use only the highest quality ingredients and our products are regularly tested for banned substances.

How To Use Performance Isolate?

One scoop of Performance Isolate mixes up effortlessly in as little as 180mL- 240mL of water, milk, or your favourite beverage.

This exceptionally pure whey formula is ready to go to work before and after training, in between meals, or any other time that you need to maximise your muscle recovery.

Over 35 years, our obsessive pursuit of the highest quality standards has only been matched by our desire to see you achieve your goals.
